ons, notamment sur <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://make.wordpress.org/core/2013/04/23/post-formats-schedules-and-philosophy/">la nouvelle interface de formats de contenu</a>,&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://make.wordpress.org/core/version-3-6-project-schedule/">le calendrier de d&eacute;veloppement</a> a subi quelques modifications. La date de sortie de WordPress 3.6 est dor&eacute;navant fix&eacute;e pour le 20 mai 2013, soit un mois plus tard que la date initiale.</p>\n<h3>Des t-shirts pour les 10 ans de WordPress</h3>\n<p><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://wordpress.org/news/2013/04/wordpress-10th-anniversary-tees/">Une &eacute;dition sp&eacute;ciale de t-shirts</a> est mise en vente pour f&ecirc;ter les 10 ans de WordPress.</p>\n<h3>CMS Day 2013</h3>\n<p><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://www.cmsday.fr/">Le CMS Day 2013</a>&nbsp;aura lieu le 25 juin 2013 &agrave; la MAS de Paris. WordPress Francophone sera repr&eacute;sent&eacute;e.</p>\n<h3>Optimisation du chargement des images</h3>\n<p><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://www.geekpress.fr/wordpress/tutoriel/chargement-dynamique-images-lazyload-1868/">Avec LazyLoad</a>, optimisez facilement le chargement des images de votre site.</p>\n<h3>Th&egrave;mes : faire le bon choix</h3>\n<p>Comment faire le bon choix de th&egrave;mes le moment venu ? <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://wpformation.com/theme-wordpress-premium-choix/">C&rsquo;est &agrave; cette question que veut r&eacute;pondre Fabrice Ducarme</a>.</p>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=KL-5o6KEApk:EzHH9RkJPgQ:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></a> <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=KL-5o6KEApk:EzHH9RkJPgQ:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?i=KL-5o6KEApk:EzHH9RkJPgQ:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></a> <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=KL-5o6KEApk:EzHH9RkJPgQ:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></a> <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=KL-5o6KEApk:EzHH9RkJPgQ:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?i=KL-5o6KEApk:EzHH9RkJPgQ:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></a>\n</div>\n<img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/WordpressFrancophone/~4/KL-5o6KEApk" height="1" width="1">\n</div>";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:68:"\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n    ";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:6:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:23:"4h18 : Wysija Vs MyMail";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:2:"id";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:33:"http://4h18.com/wysija-vs-mymail/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:2:{s:3:"rel";s:9:"alternate";s:4:"href";s:33:"http://4h18.com/wysija-vs-mymail/";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:9:"published";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:25:"2013-04-29T17:33:34+00:00";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:6:"author";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005